+  // B2c.2: resolve the tagged canvas's ID3D11Texture2D on the GPU thread via a
+  // SCANOUT-free overlay representation (a normal 2D canvas SI is DISPLAY_READ-
+  // only, so ProduceOverlay's SCANOUT gate would reject it). Hold the scoped
+  // read access alive across WeaveCanvas: it inserts the canvas-render acquire
